00:38:26,152 --> 00:38:27,985
And now...

468
00:38:28,153 --> 00:38:29,487
...let's talk seriously.

469
00:38:29,655 --> 00:38:34,034
For the entrapment, we're gonna have to ask you for four big ones, $4000.

